11.2 Will you stop using the modus-themes?
==========================================

No.  For my workflow, accessibility is the most important quality.  The
‘modus-themes’ will remain my default choice.


File: ef-themes.info,  Node: Then why develop the ef-themes?,  Prev: Will you stop using the modus-themes?,  Up: FAQ

11.3 Then why develop the ef-themes?
====================================

Because I think that users deserve “pretty” themes that (i) do make some
considerations for legibility, and (ii) are not designed on a whimsy.

   The ‘ef-themes’ are my answer to those who (i) like my
‘modus-themes’, (ii) want something with a bit more flair, and (iii) are
fine with a bit more relaxed accessibility target.


